name: WeedProject.org
body:
### Welcome to WeedProject.org
Open source cannabis data.  

```
$ cd weedproject/home
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Our Purpose
Open source tools to help developers build on top of the ever growing cannabis industry. 

### Support or Contact
Want to contribute? 
1) Fork it.
2) Make a commit on a new branch.
3) Send a pull request and we'll add it. 

Contact love@weedproject.com for questions.
